    <refsection xml:id="Description_CCS">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>This block is an ideal current source. The current value is
            controlled through the explicit input of the block (connected to standard
            Xcos blocks). The voltage across the block is independent of the current
            value.
        </para>
    </refsection>
